\begin_layout Subsubsection
Qualification and Election of Directors
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In order to be eligible to serve as a director, the individual must be 18
 years of age and an affiliate within affiliate classifications created
 by the board.
 Directors may be elected at any board meeting by the majority vote.
 The election of directors to replace those who have fulfilled their term
 of office shall take place at the annual meeting of directors as described
 in 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
